# Q&A EVIDENCE ARCHIVE — Template
# Copy this file to qa_archive_condensed.txt and populate with your own evidence.
# This archive is the source of truth for all resume claims.
# The pipeline's Archive Lookup Agent fuzzy-matches Gate 0 questions against this file.

## METRICS (universal facts — numbers, dates, counts)
Q: How many years of program management experience do you have?
A: [Your answer — e.g., "8 years total across X, Y, Z roles"]

Q: What was your team size at [Role]?
A: [Your answer — e.g., "Led a team of 6 across 3 departments"]

## FACTUAL (tools, methods, frameworks, accomplishments)
Q: What project management tools have you used?
A: [Your answer — e.g., "Jira, Asana, Smartsheet, Confluence"]

Q: Have you used any formal change management frameworks (ADKAR, LEAN, Prosci)?
A: [Your answer]

Q: What AI/LLM tools have you worked with?
A: [Your answer]

## NARRATIVE STORIES (origin stories, recognition events, leadership moments)
Q: Tell me about a time you had to influence without authority.
A: [Your answer — compressed narrative format]

Q: What was the most complex cross-functional initiative you managed?
A: [Your answer]

## CONFIRMED GAPS (things you have NOT done — prevents overclaiming)
Q: Have you managed a P&L or budget ownership?
A: [Your answer — be honest, e.g., "No direct P&L ownership"]

Q: Do you have experience with [specific certification/framework]?
A: [Your answer]
